node.text:
Wanna be VIP at my next #ChimpDinner virtually? Get a taste of all the fun on this weeks episode of #ConversationsWithCarroll when my mom @mariazwfmiami goes one on  with @nfl alum and friend to @zwfmiami @carrollcity. 

Stay tuned for announcements on my next big feast and how you can be there virtually. 
____
Catch premiere today at NOON EST by #SwipeUpnin stories and show the love in comments below 👇. 
_____
PR: @mattdillon1983

node.text:
Join us in an unforgettable 5- hour guided experience, that will completely sweep you off your feet! Spend the day interacting with an array of stunning wildlife, catered lunch, jungle music and much more that will transport you to another world! This incredible experience will surely fulfill your bucket list of dreams.
 
ZWF VIP Jungle Experience package includes:
General Wildlife Experience
Animal Presentations
Feline Experience
Primate Experience
Owl Encounter
Catered Lunch (1 hour)
Sloth Encounter
Tamandua Encounter
Watch Limbani paint (No interaction)
Big Cat Photo (Cougar)

#ZWFMiami
#Chimpanzee
#wildlifeadventure 

🎥 @alexis_canovas
@mariowildlife 
@limbanizwf 
@mariazwfmiami
@mattdillon1983
